  <brief_title>Pre-operative Preparation Using 2% Chlorhexidine Cloth For Shoulder Surgery</brief_title>
  <official_title>Efficacy of Home Pre-Operative Use of 2% Chlorhexidine Cloths Prior to Shoulder Surgery</official_title>
